reviewText: Saw it before. Wanted it for collection.

"A group of scientists returns from the West Indies where they had conducted experiments on a peculiar species of cats.  Nora, the daughter of one of the scientists, is suffering from an obsessive fear of cats and is subject to sleepwalking and nightmares about a strange catlike creature.  But Nora's dreams become a frightening reality when a gruesome murder occurs."

Made in 1948.
